The movie industry has lost one of its own, Actor Dejo Adetokunbo, popularly known as Dejo Tunfulu, to the cold hands of death. It was gathered that Dejo, who is popular in the Yoruba movie sector, had been battling with an undisclosed terminal illness about five years ago. The middle-aged actor was said to have taken a break from acting to attend to his ill health. Confirming the sad news, Yoruba movie gist by Gbolahan Adetayo, was said to have called Dejoâ€™s mobile number and a supposed family member picked the call and confirmed that indeed the actor who has featured in several movies has died.